                  Gamified reward system for Code Ninjas facilities with isolated
                  multi-tenant data, student progress sync from the Code Ninjas
                  Impact API, JWT authentication, role hierarchy, and immutable
                  ledger transactions as the source of truth for balances.
                </p>
